trans-unit.source: Become an e-commerce expert in leaps and bounds!
With all of the great features and benefits that PrestaShop offers, it's important to keep up!

trans-unit.source: The main goal of all of the features we offer is to make you succeed in the e-commerce world. In order to accomplish this, we have created a system of badges and points that make it easy to monitor your progress as a merchant. We have broken down the system into three levels, all of which are integral to success in the e-commerce world: (i) Your use of key e-commerce features on your store; (ii) Your sales performance; (iii) Your presence in international markets.
trans-unit.target: Glavni cilj svih funkcija koje nudimo je da vas učinimo uspešnim u svetu elektronske trgovine. Da bi se ovo postiglo, stvorili smo sistem bedževa i tačaka koje olakšavaju praćenje vašeg napredka kao trgovaca. Oborili smo sistem na tri nivoa, koji su svi sastavni za uspeh u svetu elektronske trgovine: (i) Korišćenje ključnih funkcija elektronske trgovine na vašoj prodavnici; (ii) Vaše prodajne performanse; (iii) Vaše prisustvo na međunarodnim tržištima.

trans-unit.source: The more progress your store makes, the more badges and points you earn. No need to submit any information or fill out any forms; we know how busy you are, everything is automatic!
trans-unit.target: Što više napretka čini vaša prodavnice, to ćete više zaraditi bedževa poena. Nema potrebe za postavljanjem bilo kakvih informacija ili za popunjavanjima ikakvih formi; Znamo koliko ste zauzeti, sve je automaski!
